Employee entity or collection 

Main path : http://localhost:9090/api/employees

get Method : to getAllEmployeeDetails 

http://localhost:9090/api/employees/getAllEmployeeDetails

get method : to get employee info using id 

http://localhost:9090/api/employees/getEmployeeById/1

http://localhost:9090/api/employees/getEmployeeById/100


post method : to store employee records 

http://localhost:9090/api/employees/employeeStore

data 
{"name":"Raju","salary":12000}



put method : update employee salary using id 

http://localhost:9090/api/employees/updateEmployeeSalary

data 
{"_id":100,"salary":24000}
{"_id":1,"salary":22000}


delete method : delete employee record by id 


http://localhost:9090/api/employees/deleteEmployeeById/1
http://localhost:9090/api/employees/deleteEmployeeById/100




